# Project Structure Guide

This is a Next.js project with a component registry system. The main structure is:

## Core Application

- [app/layout.tsx](mdc:app/layout.tsx) - Root layout component
- [app/page.tsx](mdc:app/page.tsx) - Main page component
- [app/globals.css](mdc:app/globals.css) - Global styles
- [app/favicon.ico](mdc:app/favicon.ico) - Site favicon

## Components

- [components/](mdc:components/) - Shared components
- [components/open-in-v0-button.tsx](mdc:components/open-in-v0-button.tsx) - V0 integration button

## Registry System

- [registry/](mdc:registry/) - Component registry containing all available components
- [registry.json](mdc:registry.json) - Registry configuration
- [registry/domino/](mdc:registry/domino/) - Main registry namespace
- [registry/domino/ui/](mdc:registry/domino/ui/) - Base UI components (shadcn/ui)
- [registry/domino/blocks/](mdc:registry/domino/blocks/) - Complex component blocks
- [registry/domino/hooks/](mdc:registry/domino/hooks/) - Shared hooks

## Configuration

- [package.json](mdc:package.json) - Dependencies and scripts
- [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json) - TypeScript configuration
- [next.config.ts](mdc:next.config.ts) - Next.js configuration
- [components.json](mdc:components.json) - shadcn/ui configuration

## Public Assets

- [public/](mdc:public/) - Static assets and component registry JSON files
- [public/r/](mdc:public/r/) - Component registry JSON files for each component
